<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>SocialHub - Edit Post</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

  <style>
    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 15%, rgba(56,189,248,0.18), transparent 20%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 8%, rgba(168,85,247,0.16), transparent 20%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #0b1120 0%, #0f172a 55%, #020617 100%);
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .navbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      background: rgba(7, 14, 33, 0.88);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.12);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
    }

    .navbar-inner {
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.85rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .btn-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.95rem 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.18);
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, background 0.25s ease, opacity 0.25s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: inherit;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(56,189,248,0.24);
      border-color: rgba(56,189,248,0.3);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.8);
      color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    .btn-danger {
      background: rgba(239,68,68,0.14);
      border-color: rgba(248,113,113,0.35);
      color: #fecaca;
    }

    .btn-pill:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .page-shell {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    }

    .back-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.55rem;
      margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
      color: #bae6fd;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .edit-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 760px) 280px;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .card {
      border-radius: 2rem;
      background: rgba(15,23,42,0.94);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      box-shadow: 0 40px 90px rgba(0,0,0,0.24);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    }

    .edit-card {
      padding: 2.25rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.65rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(56,189,248,0.12);
      color: #bae6fd;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      width: fit-content;
    }

    .edit-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #ffffff;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .edit-copy {
      margin: 0;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    .form-panel {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.12);
      border-radius: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .field-label {
      display: block;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .textarea {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 300px;
      border-radius: 1.75rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.16);
      background: rgba(2,6,23,0.55);
      color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem;
      resize: vertical;
      outline: none;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .textarea:focus {
      border-color: rgba(56,189,248,0.85);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(56,189,248,0.12);
    }

    .helper-text {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin: 0;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .form-actions {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 0.25rem;
    }

    .side-panel {
      position: sticky;
      top: 100px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .panel-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .panel-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0.85rem;
    }

    .panel-list li {
      padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
      border-radius: 1.25rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,0.08);
      color: #cbd5e1;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .edit-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .side-panel {
        position: static;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .navbar-inner {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .nav-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .btn-pill {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .page-shell {
        padding: 1rem 1rem 3rem;
      }

      .edit-card,
      .form-panel {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .form-actions {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .textarea {
        min-height: 240px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header class="navbar">
    <div class="navbar-inner">
      <a href="/profile" class="logo">SocialHub</a>
      <div class="nav-actions">
        <a href="/profile" class="btn-pill btn-secondary">
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
          Profile
        </a>
        <a href="/logout" class="btn-pill btn-danger">
          <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i>
          Logout
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page-shell">
    <a href="/profile" class="back-link">
      <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
      Back to feed
    </a>

    <div class="edit-layout">
      <section class="card edit-card">
        <span class="hero-label">
          <i class="fas fa-pen-to-square"></i>
          Edit Post
        </span>

        <div>
          <h1 class="edit-title">Refine your update.</h1>
          <p class="edit-copy">Update your post content and keep your SocialHub feed polished.</p>
        </div>

        <form method="post" action="/update/<%= post._id %>" class="form-panel">
          <div>
            <label for="content" class="field-label">Post Content</label>
            <textarea
              id="content"
              name="content"
              class="textarea"
              required
              placeholder="Update your post..."
            ><%= post.content %></textarea>
          </div>

          <p class="helper-text">
            <i class="fas fa-circle-info"></i>
            Make sure your post is meaningful and respectful before saving.
          </p>

          <div class="form-actions">
            <button type="submit" class="btn-pill btn-primary">
              <i class="fas fa-floppy-disk"></i>
              Save Changes
            </button>

            <a href="/profile" class="btn-pill btn-secondary">
              <i class="fas fa-xmark"></i>
              Cancel
            </a>
          </div>
        </form>
      </section>

      <aside class="card side-panel">
        <h2 class="panel-title">Editing Tips</h2>
        <ul class="panel-list">
          <li>Keep your update clear and easy to read.</li>
          <li>You can return to your feed without saving.</li>
          <li>Changes appear immediately after saving.</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>